Description: quit utility for LXDE 
 LXSession-logout is a simple utility for logout and quit a session.

Package: lxsession-default-apps
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: simple tool to configure lxsession default applications 
 lxsession-default-apps is a simple session editor GUI for lxsession default
 applications.

Package: lxsession-update-notifier-compat
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, lxsession, update-notifier-common
Provides: update-notifier
Replaces: update-notifier
Conflicts: update-notifier
Description: compatibility package for update-notifier functionnalities
 lxsession-update-notifier-compat install the needed files to replace
 update-notifier functionnalities. You also need to use update-notifier-clone
 for update-manager/command in lxsession settings.
